President Donald Trump's peace plan includes the suggestion that borders be redrawn to include 300,000 Arab citizens of Israel in a Palestinian state.
The Trump plan was announced at a time when Palestinian citizens of Israel increasingly feel painted as the enemy by Mr. Netanyahu and other hard-liners.